name: Nde Piara Our
description:
What is in your search has arrived.

Veio o que está em tua busca.

(*title written in native Tupi language)


A drawing inspired by incursions in the natural landscape of Bonito, in  Pernambuco state - Brazil. This work is also part of a series project entitled Estrela Cinnabar.

Chalk and charcoal on paper.
3163  ×  4108 px

Follow her.
